I have consumed too much coffee
  in too short order:

  It was hot
  I was cold

Too much in too short-
Shit, I drank a fucking quart

My body vibrates in retort.
&lt;/pre&gt;</content><author><name>Kyle Thomas Raymond</name></author><category term="poems" /><summary type="html">I have consumed too much coffee in too short order:</summary></entry></feed>